  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc0\u0d82\u0da0\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dc5 \u0d85\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person who defrauded rice was caught with firearms",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Special Task Force, a suspect was arrested in the banana fort area of \u200b\u200bMinuwangoda along with three firearms after obtaining rice from rice producers and defrauding them of Rs.",
        "Based on the information received regarding the suspect, the Organized Crime Unit (1) of the Special Task Force arrested the suspect and during the search of his house, they found a 12-bore firearm, two pistols and a sword, according to the task force.",
        "The suspect is a 36-year-old resident of Negombo and 15 cases of money fraud are pending against the suspect in many courts, the Special Task Force said.",
        "The suspect has been handed over to Minuwangoda Police for further investigations."
      ],
